      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Zest your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
