    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>lemon zest</strong> in a bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>gremolata</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy tomato stock</strong></p>",
